Title: Badnore a veteran parliamentarian
Content: Former Rajya Sabha MP from Rajasthan V.P. Singh Badnore, who has been appointed new Governor of Punjab, is a veteran parliamentarian who was elected to the Lok Sabha twice and was a member of the Raja
